1477
01:34:27,794 --> 01:34:29,125
PERE:
Though we cannot know...

1478
01:34:29,162 --> 01:34:31,357
Armande Voizin 's
last thoughts...

1479
01:34:32,465 --> 01:34:36,162
we can hope they were
thoughts ofpenitence.

